TextBody:
Hello Gill,
 
Thank you for contacting Netwrix Technical Support.
Before upgrading to 12.0, I suggest you upgrade to 11.6 and make sure everything is working. After successfully upgrading to 11.6, you can upgrade to 12.0.
 
Yes, we do have a KB article for the upgrade, but we strongly advise having a Netwrix engineer guide you through it step by step.
 
11.5 to 11.6 upgrade
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Install/Application/Upgrade/Wizard.htm
 
11.6 to 12.0 upgrade
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/AccessAnalyzer_12.0/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Install/Application/Upgrade/Wizard.htm
 
We strongly advise before upgrading, you take a full snapshot of both servers (StealthAUDIT and SQL)
 
Since you are on 11.5, we can have a preflight meeting to review your current settings, take screenshots, and discuss the upgrade.
 
If you want me to schedule the preflight meeting, please reply to this email and let me know.
 
Thanks,


Frantz Jean Baptiste
Technical Support T1
Phone: 1-949-407-5125 | Toll-free: 888-638-9749
